th consequences (malaria, malnutrition, diarrhoea, and inland flood-related fatalities).<sup>21</sup></p></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733158/fx1.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733161/fx2.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733227/fx3.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733236/fx4.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733239/fx5.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733164/fx6.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733242/fx7.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733245/fx8.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733248/fx9.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733167/fx10.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733170/fx11.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733173/fx12.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733176/fx13.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733179/fx14.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733182/fx15.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733185/fx16.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733188/fx17.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733191/fx18.sml"></img></div></div><div class="image"><div><img src="/cms/attachment/2001002294/2003733194/fx19.sml"></img></di